{
  "stem": "17135.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on top of this, the underground had information that there is a plan in case that the Red Army comes so close that there's danger that they will conquer Auschwitz, they should kill them all.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what a diabolic plan they had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All this was known to the underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very few people knew about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had a plan to use conquered, heavy artillery, Russian artillery that they conquered in the war, and, and, and, and Russian shells.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then by artillery, shoot it, it into rubble and kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, to the world, blame the Russians did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They knew there were camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They knew there were prisoners, but they didn't give a damn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They just wanted to, to, to [INAUDIBLE] And they wanted to destroy everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's what they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Let me put it this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All those years, there was a one, one agreement that nobody runs away with the permission of his fellow prisoners because if one ran away, in most instances, a hundred had to pay the price of this.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "By staying all night, this guy, also, Wiseman, he had to, they had to stand there too, to watch them as they were shooting people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But in case, that they knew, for the underground knew, that they will kill everybody, when the day comes, let's make organized, a mass outbreak.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Whoever gets saved gets saved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the rest, what have you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But if they anyway will implement their plan-- but the plan, all the details, it wasn't-- this SS plan was known to SS and how they found out, the underground, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But they found out about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
